##Wuhan Xiaotangshan: HOW TO BUILD 5G network by three operators

Micro signal

Function introduction, the official account of tecent science and technology of tecent news banner, read technology here!

Guo Xiaofeng is the author of "periscope" in tencent news

A new outbreak of pneumonia. Recently, the three major telecommunications operators have launched emergency communications support work to ensure smooth communications, safeguard key areas, isolation hospitals and other mobile communications network unimpeded.

Meanwhile, the construction of a 5G network and the outbreak of Split Second in Wuhan, the hardest hit area. On January 25th, the first 5G network was launched at the Vulcan Mountain Hospital. The smooth communication is the guarantee of life extension. This speed is unprecedented. For this, tecent news"periscope"connect the person in charge of building network of 3 big telecommunication operators of Wuhan, restored the whole process of building a network in the first time.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Overspeed construction of 5G base station

Back in the afternoon of January 23, Wuhan decided to build a 25,000-square-metre temporary hospital with a capacity of 1,000 beds, following the model of Beijing's Xiaotangshan Hospital during SARS in 2003. The hospital is located in the Zhiyin Lake, Caidian District, Wuhan Staff Sanatorium, named Wuhan Huoshenshan Hospital.

That night, the operator received the network task. Huoshenshan hospital is located near Zhiyin Lake in Caidian District. There is little flow of people around the hospital. The original network coverage can only guarantee voice calls, so we need to expand the capacity and increase Singi Station. The construction of a 1,000-bed hospital, plus medical, logistics and other personnel, Vulcan Mountain Hospital and the outside world is open, the latest situation of the epidemic can be transmitted in a timely manner, the network signal is the key.

Wang Yan, deputy general manager of Wuhan Mobile Network Department, told tencent news'Qianwang'that it usually takes one month to build a base station. The task is urgent and requires delivery before the main project of the hospital is completed, it's a lot of pressure.

"At 18:00 on the night of January 23, I received the mission notice. I was arranging the task of network support for epidemic prevention and control. As soon as I heard the news, I immediately became nervous. At the last minute, people in the group were told to gather nearby, and many people were told that they had signed up enthusiastically for the support. At last, a dozen people were called in and were already on their way to Caidian District by 18:30,"said Wang Yan.

At the same time, Wuhan Telecom, Wuhan Unicom has also set out. According to "prospect" of tencent news, due to the principle of joint construction and sharing of base stations, the construction of the three major operators in Singi Station is being carried out together with the Tower Company, which provides the tower houses and supporting facilities, the three major operators are responsible for site selection and installation, while Huawei and ZTE provide base station equipment and technical support.

On January 24, Caidian District had sleet. The cold weather made the road muddy and slippery. Zeng, a maintenance worker at Wuhan Mobile Caidian District, has worked for nearly 40 hours at the Vulcan Mountain Hospital. "The installation of the equipment requires climbing to the top of the tower. Because of the rain, it will be much more difficult to get to the tower. Normally it takes only two hours to install the equipment, and today it took six hours, " Zeng said, "But I don't feel tired. I just want to do something for Wuhan. If I hurry, I can save more people. "

The same morning, China Unicom Wuhan Branch Network Planning and construction personnel also first time arrived at Wuhan Caidian Huoshenshan Hospital Construction Site, communications network construction fully started.

The head of the Network Development Department of Wuhan Unicom told tencent news'prospect'that, "The assignment was very urgent, and the family was very worried, and still is. On the same day, we arranged for the relevant people to go to the scene for an inspection, because it was in the suburbs and the roads were slippery in the dark. It was very difficult. "

At 1200 hours on January 25, the first 5G base station was robbed by the Fire God Mountain Hospital in Caidian. Boom, boom, boom, boom, boom. 'We finished the base station in less than two days, which is hard to imagine, ' Wang Yan told tencent news' Qianwang.

That night, China Unicom formally completed the test base station, announced the opening. In only 36 hours, the 3G / 4G / 5g network of Huoshenshan Hospital was put into operation, and the whole process of survey, planning, design, construction, adjustment, commissioning and optimization of a new base station was completed, three full days ahead of schedule, to better control the outbreak of the precious time saved.

At 15:00 pm on January 26, all four base stations of CAIDIAN Huoshenshan Hospital of Wuhan Mobile were opened, 2G, 4g and 5G signals were fully loaded, the actual measured speed was 800 mbps, and could accommodate nearly 20,000 people for simultaneous online communication.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
I forgot about Spring Festival

On the evening of January 23, the Wuhan Branch of China Telecom received a notice from the city's emergency command for epidemic prevention and control, requesting the Wuhan Branch of China Telecom to complete the construction of 4G and 5G coverage of CAIDIAN Huoshenshan wireless network within three days.

Wuhan Telecom in charge of Construction Shi Jun deputy general manager of Tencent News, "periscope" line, said the first time the task of organizing the relevant departments to start network planning. "Frankly, not being afraid is fake, but I can't think of that much. Time is short and party members rush forward. "

On the night of January 23, the construction units of Wuhan Telecom began the sudden construction of 4G, 5G base station and main optical cable connecting to the hospital. After a continuous day-and-night intensity operation, by 1600 hours on the afternoon of January 24, the 24-core is connected to the main dry optical cable for completion, one day ahead of schedule; by 18 hours on the 24th high supporting rods, 20 places have been completed, and Start 4G, 5G equipment hanging station, power box construction. All the fiber cables are laid at night; at 20 hours, 5g of Zhangjiadu base station is opened successfully. Before you kill him

"This time it's different, it's very difficult. First of all, we need cold weather operations. Second, we need to keep the cables from being damaged by other construction projects on the site at all times. Second, we need to keep the power supply from going wrong. So we have more than 40 people working three shifts 24 hours a day, and we have forgotten about the Spring Festival,"Shi said.

January 25 at 10:00, all the hospital base station antenna support Rod 24 completed construction. At 1139 hours the ticking will complete the installation of the power box and start the power supply. Base station equipment installed at noon on the 25th. All 4g and 5G base stations opened in the afternoon of the 25th. Before you kill him

Different from the other two operators, Wuhan Telecom in addition to the base station task, there is a key task. According to Shi Jun, after the first stage of network construction is completed, the next stage of work is focused on the delivery of the main project in the hospital, the start of the hospital information construction.

"first, we need to build a medical network, and at the same time, we need to use cloud services as the cornerstone and do a good job in providing application services, so as to improve the efficiency of medical care through the linkage of the network, cloud and application, " Shi said.

On the afternoon of January 25, the control and Prevention Headquarters of the pneumonia epidemic in Wuhan COVID-19 held a meeting and decided to build another "Little Tangshan" hospital -- Foshan Thor Mountain Hospital. The hospital, located in Huangjiahu, Jiangxia district, Wuhan, will provide 1,500 additional beds with a capacity of 2,000 medical staff.

For the "Xiaotangshan Hospital" in operation on January 27 with good communication conditions, China Tower Huanggang Branch after receiving the task to actively communicate with the three operators to determine the program, at present, on the basis of the completed large-scale indoor network main body project, the urgent construction carries on the equipment survey, ensures when the hospital main body project delivers, the communication is unimpeded.

Compared with the Vulcan Mountain Hospital, the location of the hospital is because many 5g base stations were already deployed during the 7th Military Games, the leaders of the three operators told tencent news'periscope, so the overall construction and coverage is better, the follow-up will be expanded according to the situation.

In addition to network construction, the three major operators also launched a series of emergency communications and network support services. Such as to support the epidemic prevention and disaster relief personnel to provide non-shutdown, emergency start-up and other services, to protect the epidemic prevention and control front-line personnel and users of normal communications, and so on. In the face of an epidemic, roads can be blocked, but communications must not be cut off.
